
# Arquivo de Configuração do Apache - Padrão de Instalação |   # Arquivo de Hardening do Apache
                                                           | ServerTokens Prod
ServerRoot "/etc/httpd"                                    | ServerSignature Off
PidFile /var/run/httpd.pid                                 | Timeout 60
Timeout 300                                                | KeepAlive On
KeepAlive On                                               | MaxKeepAliveRequests 50
MaxKeepAliveRequests 100                                   | KeepAliveTimeout 3
KeepAliveTimeout 5                                         | TraceEnable Off
Listen 80                                                  | FileETag None
ServerTokens Full                                          | Header always unset X-Powered-By                                                
ServerSignature On                                         | <Directory />
TraceEnable On                                             |     AllowOverride None
User apache                                                |     Require all denied
Group apache                                               |     Options -Indexes -FollowSymLinks -ExecCGI
DocumentRoot "/var/www/html"                               | <Directory "/var/www/html">
<Directory />                                              |     Options -Indexes -FollowSymLinks -ExecCGI
    AllowOverride none                                     |     AllowOverride None
    Require all denied                                     |      Require all granted
</Directory>                                               | </Directory>
<Directory "/var/www/html">                                | Header edit Set-Cookie ^(.*)$ $1;HttpOnly;Secure
    Options Indexes FollowSymLinks                         | ErrorLog "logs/error_log"
    AllowOverride None                                     | LogLevel error
    Require all granted                                    | CustomLog "logs/access_log" combined
</Directory>                                               | 
ErrorLog "logs/error_log"                                  |
LogLevel warn                                              |
CustomLog "logs/access_log" combined                       |
<IfModule dir_module>                                      |
    DirectoryIndex index.html                              |
</IfModule>                                                |
